*:'''Homophones''': [[break]]

===Noun===
'''brake'''

# A [[device]] used to [[slow]] or [[stop]] a [[vehicle]], by [[friction]]; often [[installed]] on the [[wheel]]s.
# something that slows or stops and [[action]]
#{{nautical}} the [[handle]], [[manned]] by up to six men, by which a [[ship]]'s [[pump]] was [[worked]]
# a [[thicket]], or an area [[overgrown]] with [[brier]]s etc.

